class=\"language-text\">Consumer</code>가 가장 중요한 요소입니다.</p>\n<p>모든 작업은 비동기로 처리되며 이벤트에 대한 조율이 필요 없습니다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1231 832' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-8902cc3722d514c0e2c687ff6d1d70d9'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-8902cc3722d514c0e2c687ff6d1d70d9)' width='1231' height='832' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAArCAIAAABHOBkQAAAACXBIWXMAADIjAAAyIwHN55PYAAAR50lEQVRo3q1ZaWxbV3ZWArSdAYr2R4EWBTqZQZuknaYZFDOYFmjnx6AB2gyKAl2ng2I6iOPYcSZIvMSWLVuiFi4ixX0nH/f9vcddpLiK%2byLJkrXb1kbtq21J1r5S7CGfzcixZavJXBxcXJ73%2bO757j3n3O%2b8V1H4zbXV1dUHDx48fGl79OjR4eHhC/9%2bdHQE/eLCQiYZbUvHs6lYOhGBMQyyyWg6GYVxJhElrkI/NzcH91d8c7uJiZeWlkKhUF9fX1dX150TGlyNRqMDAwNwfz6ff/5JoArY1cvd2GqfY6XPsTPkBVntd64PuneGW7bue7aHvNCDZrkbN8hYj9c2Kp63Jn9CIww9CcDExMTg4OAJln1528LCAiA56bb9w6OYW12YjezmQmmHsKtF1umVRjFOm0vY40d6A8r%2boKo/pMpPRQsLcZWgYWJqpuKF03yNHZicnLx79y4MNjY2tp9tOzs7jx8/zuVyBIDu7u6TABwAAJe6MNO6P%2bId8Ik77Nw7zYLxhHY8bepw8rpcvA4HZ8Avyed8hfmY%2boUADo%2bOhkZH%2bvv7B/oHBvv7BwcGQAYGB/t6e6dKPpc/PPzKzhA%2bDTtAAHi8/GBhenJxdrosS3Mzs5Pj46PDRRdfWiJ24ODg4Lkdzu8d5NNe3f2YXq3XYg4rZsfMVtxuUT7ownxOA4xBg9lxpVbdF1LrReRnAORLdmTcbsV337R9/wfWd38Igr71DvYX72Lf/4H97Xf4P/rbu/fulVw1//wOwAKPjI5ub67/%2bKr6Dy9av3MF/5PLX8obV%2b3/SLZ29A6uP37cdbILgQVJF2I2KsmmKBuP1chsNGOIrLAxbl5g6D1Ma5Ks8VC0HoqxlcmkCchXpmfnvwRwVALg5/JCf/RG11/%2bdfdP/mH0k89HPvpk9MJnbX/%2bbu9f/dD4nT9lUKn9AwPHwxTG4PrNzc3/9P77E5OTszNTv/s/8oqzLa996K4AOeOq%2bKAor59vebPKYw3Ed7c2MdwKO/yVh/T09GQy6V/%2b6gwmqXdiqnpdgGH0NSgdTLS1WqClXz/L0NiYWJSqbabpPBRDsL72BrfhWQDEDgTkiOH3/iD0vbf9b70T/clPW3/8d5G/%2bfuWN95s/e5bvD9%2bQ6vRrq2tHc%2bVMF5eXp6fn3c6nffv34cnWINJjiUgxEMia1jmSsjcCYE1zEGDakdoa3sL0mg8Hl9fX4esRTxhcRHcagmeMzc3m8q0RR3KuXZTU%2b0V8q1LNNJlcvUlbt3F2XazQ