bernetes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Event-Driven Architecture for Cloud-Native in Kubernetes</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.theodo.com/2019/08/event-driven-architectures-rabbitmq/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Introduction to Event-driven Architectures With RabbitMQ</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/software-architecture-patterns/9781491971437/ch02.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Event-Driven Architecture</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://jaehue.github.io/post/event-driven/#fn:3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">내 멋대로 구현한 이벤트 드리븐</a></p>\n</span>\n","tags":[{"title":"이벤트 드리븐","path":"/tag/%EC%9D%B4%EB%B2%A4%ED%8A%B8%20%EB%93%9C%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%90/"},{"title":"아키텍처","path":"/tag/%EC%95%84%ED%82%A4%ED%85%8D%EC%B2%98/"},{"title":"Event Driven","path":"/tag/Event%20Driven/"},{"title":"Architecture","path":"/tag/Architecture/"}],"date":"2월 10 수, 2021","update_date":"2월 10 수, 2021","timeToRead":7,"headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"EDA(Eventt Driven Architecture)란?","anchor":"#edaeventt-driven-architecture란"},{"depth":2,"value":"EDA의 구성요소","anchor":"#eda의-구성요소"},{"depth":2,"value":"EDA의 동작 방식","anchor":"#eda의-동작-방식"},{"depth":3,"value":"Event Processing Style","anchor":"#event-processing-style"},{"depth":2,"value":"토폴로지 구성","anchor":"#토폴로지-구성"},{"depth":2,"value":"EDA의 장단점","anchor":"#eda의-장단점"},{"depth":3,"value":"장점","anchor":"#장점"},{"depth":3,"value":"단점","anchor":"#단점"},{"depth":2,"value":"EDA를 선택할 때 고려할 특징","anchor":"#eda를-선택할-때-고려할-특징"},{"depth":2,"value":"요약","anchor":"#요약"},{"depth":2,"value":"Reference","anchor":"#reference"}]},"related":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"MSA(Microservice Architecture)이란?","category":"프로그래밍","description":"마이크로 서비스 아키텍처에 대하여 정리합니다.","path":"/what-is-msa/","date":"2021.02.24"}},{"node":{"title":"동시성과 병렬성","category":"프로그래밍","description":"동시성과 병렬성의 특징을 알아봅니다.","path":"/cuncurrency-parallelism/","date":"2021.0